{"tid":901563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重溫！不是旅遊　是來生活　一小時生活圈　可塞至少１億人的香港","createTime":"2018-11-14T06:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T05:21:57.000Z","uid":47714,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2794b0bd2945550ddee85231791f10f23670e395","tid":901563,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&d=NFFS3mC8m57zLGIwnaKavROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=000554cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&h=488fe8d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/nt/images/993/1_2009072010420909376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnt%2Fimages%2F993%2F1_2009072010420909376.jpg&h=75e877cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唐英年接受本報專訪時，就描繪了一幅粵港融合的遠景。他認為，香港的出路，在於一國兩制《基本法》框架下的融合發展觀。朝着粵港融合的目標前進，香港的巿場規模可以由現在七百萬人口擴展至一億人口；香港人可以選擇一個更便宜更優質的生活環境，而在「一加一大於二」的優勢互補下，珠三角可以成為全國最具經濟活力的區域。<br />\n<br />\n　　剛剛走訪完珠三角九巿的唐英年，接受本報訪問，解釋今次走訪九巿的背景。他指出，國務院發表的《珠江三角洲地區改革發展規劃綱要》，是將粵港合作提升到國家層次，成為國家的戰略安排。他相信，連同港澳兩地，珠三角區有潛質可以成為全國最具經濟活力的經濟區，「單是廣東省已有九千萬人口，再加上港澳兩地，即共有接近一億人，是相當具規模的經濟容量，可以說是一個接近中型國家的經濟容量&hellip;&hellip;連同香港的生產總值比長三角還要高，我覺得我們是有潛質做全國最具經濟活力的一個區。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_140528/20140528_e5d20716ef895239c59fjCvMkkzDGN6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_140528%2F20140528_e5d20716ef895239c59fjCvMkkzDGN6I.jpg&h=293e630f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有高鐵<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20151012/large/a1802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20151012%2Flarge%2Fa1802a.gif&h=efb74c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國客：香港是後花園　以後不計劃了　隨時來　隨便來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&d=NFFS3mC8m57zLGIwnaKavROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e4883b94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&h=85f4fa53\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20181004/480pix/1538660222_61d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20181004%2F480pix%2F1538660222_61d5.jpg&h=4e9b412e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李先生表示，高鐵開通增加其來港意慾：「因為它就像我們的後花園一樣，在整個珠三角，沒有一個城市能比得上香港的服務、美食和購物。以後想來就來，因為隨著這麼方便的高鐵開通以後，我們曾經要做的訪港計劃是不需要了，因為隨時可以買到票就可以走，不像以前我們還要計劃『十一』、『五一』這樣。」內地遊客郭先生亦表示高鐵很方便，但因為大部分時間也在穿過山洞，看不到風景，感覺比較像乘地鐵。"},{"pid":"8eb357466e1afead561070a9846facd24d94e79b","tid":901563,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"高鐵全部完成後就可塞至少14億人o既香港"},{"pid":"8e7da7b50ec08edaedd69957bcc9e03ee3b40b43","tid":901563,"uid":147367,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"1億人過黎食飯盒買豉油同屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa374849d7b1b1038a1510fd8b463f4bafdbec09","tid":901563,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"巿場規模=/=人口規模"},{"pid":"8ecd831b7140e7e1133c701930a08d7aaa50bb21","tid":901563,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"香港=中國人的免稅便利店"},{"pid":"bd84de3f03819b91919abbe761ca4fa80377c272","tid":901563,"uid":